    "The main research questions that we want to answer are the following:",
    "• What are the key security features and capabilities offered by open-source SIEM solutions, and how do they compare to commercial SIEM solutions?",
    "• What are the performance benchmarks of different open-source SIEM solutions under high traffic load and event data volume?",
    "• What are the scalability limitations of open-source SIEM solutions, and how do they perform as the size and complexity of the monitored network infrastructure grow?",
    "• How do open-source SIEM solutions address compliance and regulatory requirements, and what kind of reports do they provide for auditing purposes?"
  ],
